txt.en: 'Talk to me to become an \qAcquaintance\q with the Men of the Wold.'
'\qAcquaintance\q with the Men of the Wold, coming right up! Soon enough those guards won't be kicking you out of town (unless you liked that as an easy way to get to the stable-master that is...)'
Those guards in Harwick... I tell ya... They are not a fan of.. well... anyone but the folk of Harwick.
